Package: mapindia
Type: Package
Title: Plot Map of Indian Subcontinent
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Shubham", "Dutta", , "shubhamdutta26@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8484-0717"))
Maintainer: Shubham Dutta <shubhamdutta26@gmail.com>
Description: Get map data frames for india with different region levels 
    (e.g., district, state). The package also offers convenience functions for 
    plotting choropleths, visualizing spatial data, and handling state/district
    codes.
